# Wallupi — Implementation Plan

A UPI-style payment application with integrated AI-powered fraud prevention. Mock banking, real fraud detection logic.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Flutter SDK**: This plan assumes you have Flutter SDK installed and configured. Please confirm you have:
> - Flutter SDK installed (`flutter --version`)
> - Android Studio or an Android emulator available
> - Python 3.x installed for the Flask backend

> [!WARNING]
> **SMS & Call State**: The `telephony` and `phone_state` packages require Android. For the prototype, we'll implement manual SMS input simulation alongside the package integration so it works on emulators too.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **QR Code Scanner**: The `mobile_scanner` package requires a camera. On emulators without camera, we'll provide a mock QR input fallback.

